.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Hobby: singing, video-games, board-games, cooking, magic-tricks
Movie-Genre: satire, documentary, fantasy, mystery, horror
Job: journalist, electrician, freelancer, lawyer, librarian
House: colonial, farmhouse, townhouse, craftsman, gothic-revival

1. Hobby:singing == Color:red
2. Hobby:video-games == House:colonial
3. Job:journalist == Color:green
4. Hobby:board-games == Job:electrician
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Movie-Genre:satire == House:gothic-revival
7. Movie-Genre:documentary == Color:yellow
8. Job:freelancer is in the middle
9. Hobby:cooking is on the far left
10. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the left or right of House:farmhouse
11. Movie-Genre:documentary is to the left or right of House:craftsman
12. Movie-Genre:mystery == Job:lawyer
13. Hobby:magic-tricks == Movie-Genre:horror
14. Hobby:cooking is to the left or right of Color:blue

